import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np

x = np.linspace(0, 10, 100)
y = np.sin(x)

plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
plt.plot(x, y, label='sin(x)')
plt.title('Sine Wave')
plt.xlabel('x')
plt.ylabel('sin(x)')
plt.legend()

plt.show()
